Exit to Eden;;1994;;R;;Comedy,Crime,Romance;;4.3;;Garry Marshall;;Dana Delany,Dan Aykroyd,Rosie O'Donnell,Paul Mercurio,Hector Elizondo,Stuart Wilson,Iman,Sean O'Bryan,Stephanie Niznik,Phil Redrow,Sandra Taylor,Julie Hughes,Laurelle Mehus,Tom Hines,Alison Moir,Deborah Pratt,Laura Harring,James Patrick Stuart;;Elliot is going to the island of Eden to live out his submissive fantasies, but inadvertently photographs diamond smugglers at work. Smugglers, and detectives, follow him to the island, where they try to retrieve the film. Elliot begins falling in love with Lisa, the head mistress of the island, and Lisa must evaluate her feelings about Elliot and her own motivations.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0109758/